<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>Proposing something genuinely new while following a strict brand styleguide is not a contradiction, but it does require patience. Over several months, working with a team of UI/UX specialists, we developed new key visuals, features and interactive patterns for FPT Industrial's digital platform.</p>
    <p>I used Figma at full capacity on this one. Nothing was left approximate because the goal was to set a long-term direction for the platform, not just deliver a round of assets. Every decision was documented and reasoned.</p>
